COMP.6210 - Web Services and Design Methodologies - S2 - TG - 2018


Course Aim:

    We will be learning several new languages

  • html
  • JavaScript + Libraries
  • CSS libraries
  • Bootstrap

  • We will also use MySQL to talk to a database
  • We will also be using some new (to use) web protocols SOAP and REST

Assessment 1 Project 7/09/2018 30%
Assessment 2 Project 26/10/2018 40%
Exam Report 20/11/2018 40%
